:: StoryTitle
The Secret Next Door v4 (5-Painting Edition)


:: StoryData
{
  "ifid": "61D77317-38B1-4FD1-9B4D-1B5FC0A13728",
  "format": "Harlowe",
  "format-version": "3.3.9",
