“Look down,” she says. “At the ground, by my feet. Tell me what you see there.”
You lean in and look at the real painting on the wall.

[[Broken musical instruments.->PAINT1Fact]]
[[A basket of flowers.->PAINT1Retry]]
[[Some gold coins.->PAINT1Retry]]


:: PAINT1Retry {"position":"540,270","size":"160,120"}
<div style="text-align: center; margin: 5px 0;">
    <div style="display: inline-block; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 2px; border: 1px solid #d4af37; font-size: 0;">
        
        <img class="cecilia-cinema-zoom" 
             src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YixuanQu/Digital-heritage-and-multimedia/main/img/ESTASI%20DI%20SANTA%20CECILIA%20FRA%20I%20SANTI%20PAOLO%2C%20GIOVANNI%20EVANGELISTA%2C%20AGOSTINO%20E%20MARIA%20MADDALENA.jpg" 
             style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0; transform-origin: center bottom;">
             
        <div class="bottom-detail-glow"></div>
        
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    @keyframes pureSlowZoom {
