:: PReveal {"position":"975,950","size":"160,120"}
<div id="dynamic-map" data-progress="5" style="height: 400px; width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; margin: 5px 0; z-index: 1; border: 1px solid #ddd;"></div>
<script>
setTimeout(function() {
    var mapElement = document.getElementById('dynamic-map');
    
    if (typeof L !== 'undefined' && mapElement) {
        
        // Read progress string and parse into an integer smoothly
        var currentProgress = parseInt(mapElement.getAttribute('data-progress'), 10);
        if (isNaN(currentProgress)) { currentProgress = 0; }

        // HARD BOUNDARIES: Locked zoom between 14 and 16, disabled double-click zoom
        var map = L.map('dynamic-map', {
            minZoom: 14,
            maxZoom: 16,
            doubleClickZoom: false
        }).setView([44.49513, 11.34077], 14);

        // Retro Parchment/Grey-scale Basemap Layer
        L.tileLayer('https://{s}.basemaps.cartocdn.com/light_all/{z}/{x}/{y}{r}.png', {
            attribution: '© OpenStreetMap, © CARTO',
            maxZoom: 20
        }).addTo(map);

        // --- Marker Styles ---
        var awakeStyle = {
            color: '#D4AF37',     // Metallic Gold Border
            fillColor: '#FFD700', // Bright Gold Fill
            fillOpacity: 0.9,
            radius: 9,
            weight: 3
        };

        var sleepingStyle = {
            color: '#2C3E50',     // Dark Slate Blue Border for high contrast
            fillColor: '#7F8C8D', // Solid Muted Charcoal Grey
            fillOpacity: 0.75,
            radius: 7,
            weight: 2
        };

        // --- Database of 5 historic churches ---
        var churches = [
            {
                name: "Church of San Giovanni in Monte",
                coords: [44.49182, 11.34861],
                popupText: "<b>Painting 1: Saint Cecilia</b><br>San Giovanni in Monte<br><i>Status: Awakened!</i>"
            },
            {
                name: "Basilica of San Francesco",
                coords: [44.49492, 11.33522],
                popupText: "<b>Painting 2: Saint Paul</b><br>Basilica of San Francesco<br><i>Status: Awakened!</i>"
            },
            {
                name: "Church of Santi Gregorio e Siro",
                coords: [44.49591, 11.34246],
                popupText: "<b>Painting 3: Saint William</b><br>Santi Gregorio e Siro<br><i>Status: Awakened!</i>"
            },
            {
                name: "Church of Sant'Antonio Abate",
                coords: [44.49605, 11.33878],
                popupText: "<b>Painting 4: Saint Anthony</b><br>Sant'Antonio Abate<br><i>Status: Awakened!</i>"
            },
            {
                name: "Basilica of San Domenico",
                coords: [44.48967, 11.34444],
                popupText: "<b>Painting 5: Innocent Children</b><br>Basilica of San Domenico<br><i>Status: Awakened!</i>"
            }
        ];

        // --- App Starting Point (Gallery Hub) ---
        var galleryCoords = [44.49754, 11.35239];
        
        // Background anchor ring for Gallery Hub
        L.circleMarker(galleryCoords, { color: '#000', weight: 1, radius: 12, fill: false }).addTo(map);
        
        L.circleMarker(galleryCoords, {
            color: '#1A252F',
            fillColor: '#2C3E50',
            fillOpacity: 0.9,
            radius: 7,
            weight: 2
        }).addTo(map).bindPopup("<b>Pinacoteca Nazionale di Bologna</b><br>The Memory Hub.");

        // --- Render States Loop ---
        churches.forEach(function(church, index) {
            if (index < currentProgress) {
                // 1. Awakened State: Only renders the golden marker, NO polyline link
                var dot = L.circleMarker(church.coords, awakeStyle).addTo(map);
                dot.bindPopup(church.popupText);
            } 
            else {
                // 2. Locked State: Renders outer anchor ring and solid grey core marker
                L.circleMarker(church.coords, {
                    color: '#BDC3C7',
                    weight: 1,
                    radius: 11,
                    fill: false
                }).addTo(map);

                var dot = L.circleMarker(church.coords, sleepingStyle).addTo(map);
                dot.bindPopup("<b>Locked Memory</b><br>Keep exploring to reveal these coordinates.");
            }
        });
    }
}, 350);
</script>
You wake the fifth painting. The last dark dot lights up. Then the map does something.
One by one, lines stretch from every painting to every church — until the whole city is covered with light.
Five paintings. Five homes. One Bologna. All five voices speak together, softly: “We are not old pictures on a wall. We are the memory of this city's lost churches. And today, you remembered us.”

[[See your result.->PShare]]


:: PShare {"position":"1200,950","size":"160,120"}
''SCREEN:'' //A result card with the full glowing map and your name.//
''MEDIA:'' //A shareable card. A live public counter.//

The screen shows you a card: your full map, glowing, with one line under it — “I found the Secret Next Door.”
“You are the 2,148th person to find the secret this month,” her voice says.
“Show a friend. The next student walking past outside could be the one who brings the next painting home.”

